HEADWORD: Paripinnate
<hw>Par`i*pin"nate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Pari-</ets> + <ets>pinnate</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
